Sentencas: The Gd(1-x)A(x)Mn(1-y)CO(y)O(3-delta) (A = Sr, Ca) systems were examined as a cathode for use in solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Gd1-xAxMn1-yCoyO3-δ (A = Sr, Ca) as a cathode for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity and cathodic polarization on an 8 mol % yttria-stabilized zirconia (8YSZ) electrolyte had acceptable values for certain compositions.
Titulo: Gd1-xAxMn1-yCoyO3-δ (A = Sr, Ca) as a cathode for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thermal expansion measurements were taken, showing compatibility of Mn-rich compositions with the 8YSZ electrolyte.
Titulo: Gd1-xAxMn1-yCoyO3-δ (A = Sr, Ca) as a cathode for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Reactivity with 8YSZ revealed the formation of SrZrO3 or CaZrO3 at lower temperatures for high Co containing compositions.
Titulo: Gd1-xAxMn1-yCoyO3-δ (A = Sr, Ca) as a cathode for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: No reaction product was detected between Gd0.8Ca0.2Mn1-yCoyO3-delta and 8YSZ.
Titulo: Gd1-xAxMn1-yCoyO3-δ (A = Sr, Ca) as a cathode for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However, significant diffusion of Co into 8YSZ was found at the Gd0.8Ca0.2Mn0.4Co0.6O3-delta/8YSZ interface after annealing at 1200 degrees C for 24 h. (C) 1999 The Electrochemical Society.
Titulo: Gd1-xAxMn1-yCoyO3-δ (A = Sr, Ca) as a cathode for solid-oxide fuel cells
